OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776265866
OL,3,C'Rapid review' into Isle of Man's
OL,4,Clargest hospital commissioned
OL,6,FA "rapid review" into a major hospital
OL,7,Fhas been commissioned after doctors
OL,8,Fwarned their inpatient bed capacity
OL,9,Fhad almost been slashed in half over
OL,10,Fthe course of five years.
OL,12,FThe Isle of Man's Department of Health
OL,13,Fand Social Care announced the
OL,14,Findependent review into Noble's
OL,15,FHospital on 14 April 2026, which will
OL,16,Flook into the overall bed capacity and
OL,17,Fwhat measures could be taken to ease
OL,18,Fpressures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
