PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776265866
OL,3,C'Rapid review' into Isle of Man's
OL,4,Clargest hospital commissioned
OL,6,FA group of 75 members of senior staff
OL,7,Foutlined their concerns at a Medical
OL,8,FStaff Committee (MSC) meeting in March
OL,9,F2026, citing a "critical shortfall in
OL,10,Finpatient bed capacity".
OL,12,FThe group says Noble's Hospital
OL,13,Foperated with 314 beds in 2021, but
OL,14,Fsince then has seen a 46% decrease in
OL,15,Fcapacity to 168.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776265866
OL,3,C'Rapid review' into Isle of Man's
OL,4,Clargest hospital commissioned
OL,6,FThe staff members warned the
OL,7,Fhospital's current capacity is
OL,8,F"insufficient to safely support the
OL,9,Fsimultaneous demands of emergency
OL,10,Fadmissions and planned surgical
OL,11,Fprocedures" and called for "immediate
OL,12,Fgovernment intervention".
OL,14,FManx Care has previously insisted the
OL,15,F"service is safe" and disputed the
OL,16,Fgroup's figures. Instead, they say the
OL,17,Ftotal number of beds available has
OL,18,Fdropped from 279 to 233 since 2021 - a
OL,19,F16.5% reduction.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776265866
OL,3,C'Rapid review' into Isle of Man's
OL,4,Clargest hospital commissioned
OL,6,FDespite this, the Manx Government has
OL,7,Fnow commissioned the independent
OL,8,Freview to address the concerns and
OL,9,Ffind a way forward.
OL,11,FHealth and Social Care Minister Claire
OL,12,FChristian said: "The review builds on
OL,13,Frecent engagement with the Medical
OL,14,FStaffing Committee (MSC) and Manx
OL,15,FCare's initial actions to manage and
OL,16,Fmitigate pressures on hospital bed
OL,17,Fcapacity and ensure services remain
OL,18,Fsafe, high quality and responsive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776265866
OL,3,C'Rapid review' into Isle of Man's
OL,4,Clargest hospital commissioned
OL,6,F"With the collaboration of a small
OL,7,Fworking group consisting of frontline
OL,8,Fclinicians, the Manx Care Board,
OL,9,FMedical Staffing Committee and the
OL,10,FBritish Medical Association, the
OL,11,Freview will reflect key stakeholder
OL,12,Fand professional input."
OL,14,FThe Manx Government says they are
OL,15,Falready in the process of bringing in
OL,16,Fa number of measures to ease pressures
OL,17,Fon Noble's Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
